{"word":"ἐπαναφέρω","slug":"ἐπαναφέρω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπαναφέρω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:poetically'>poet.</a> <el>-αμφέρω</el>) (<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-ανοίσω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to throw back upon, ascribe, refer</i>, <el>τι τίνι</el> or <el>εἴς τινα</el> <b>Solon.</b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to put into the account</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><i>to bring back a message</i>, in <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a> <i>to come back, return</i>, <el>ἐπί τι</el> <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to rise</i>, as an exhalation, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}